 * badge          string   â€” e.g. "ðŸŽ¨ Web Design Services"
 * heroH1         string   â€” plain text part of h1 (before highlight)
 * heroHighlight  string   â€” gradient text part
 * heroDesc       string   â€” paragraph under h1
 * heroStats      { value: string; label: string }[]  â€” 3 inline stats
 * formTitle      string   â€” mini form card title
 * formSub        string   â€” mini form card subtitle
 * formTypeLabel  string   â€” label for the type select (default "What do you need?")
 * formTypeOptions string[] â€” options for the type select
 *
 * SECTION LABELS / TITLES (Sections 2-12)
 * â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
 * All accept default slot children via named slots for maximum flexibility.
 * Fixed section labels/titles are passed as props.
 *
 * SECTION 2 â€” featureCards: FeatureCard[]
 * SECTION 3 â€” problemCards: ProblemCard[]
 * SECTION 4 â€” processSteps: ProcessStep[]
 * SECTION 5 â€” deliverables: Deliverable[]
 * SECTION 6 â€” comparisonRows: ComparisonRow[]  (table rows)
 * SECTION 7 â€” pricingTiers: PricingTier[]
 * SECTION 8 â€” portfolioCards: PortfolioCard[]
